createTransactionEntry(bytes32,address,a.details: Establishes a new transaction entry in the ledger

params._prevTransaction: Hash of the previous transaction to maintain continuity

getAllTransactions().details: Fetch all the transaction entries recorded in the ledger

returns._0: Array containing all the transactions in the ledger

getAllTransactionsCount().details: Retrieves the total count of transactions in the ledger

getTransaction(uint256).details: Fetches the details of a specific transaction by its index

params.id: Index of the transaction to fetch

returns._0: Transaction details: hash, source address, destination address, previous transaction, latitude, longitude, timestamp

createTransactionEntry(bytes32,address,a.notice: Increases the total transaction count and emits an event at the end. Validates previous transaction for all transactions other than the first one.
